<info>
<keywords>
FTP
</keywords>
</info>

# Server-side
<reply>
<servercmd>
REPLY PASV 227 Entering Passiv Mode (1216,256,2,127,127,127)
</servercmd>
</reply>

# Client-side
<client>
<server>
ftp
</server>
 <name>
FTP getting bad host in 227-response to PASV
 </name>
